story.storyDescription: Jack's enthusiasm is cute at first...but then just gets super-creepy and weird.
story.title: 20 Questions

messages.text: hey you...ready for our date later? :)
can’t tell bc then it won’t be a surprise! :)
pretty please with a cherry on top
haha ok :) how about a game of 20 questions?
see if you can guess where I’m taking you tonight ;)
ok outdoors, um is it an event?
I was just thinking out loud with that one!
does the place involve physical activity?
is it somewhere with a lot of people?
is it somewhere we’ve been together before?
is there a body of water at this place?
this really is a mystery spot...
is it past the train tracks?
what’s past the train tracks surrounded by woods?
or just give up and wait for the surprise tonight! :)
10 more questions and then ill wait :p
like acres upon acres of land big
Is there something to do at the spot? other than walk and look around?
haha I know what you’re thinking of
OMG WHAT ELSE IS OVER THERE???!!!
is it somewhere people are allowed?
you’re going to find out later anyhow!
haha ok..if it means that much to you :p
u want to play hangman now?
YES. how many letters is the place?
hmmmm idk that’s not how 20 questions works
and you’d be even more wonderful if you gave me how many letters it is!
I was hoping it’d be 4 or 5
are we going there late at night because that’s when it’s best to go?
but for the purpose of the night, yes it’s best
most people go during the day
are there flowers at this place?
I think there are some now
is there a fence around the place?
I think I know where we’re going
maybe it’s not where I’m thinking
because the place I’m thinking of isn’t romantic
maybe you shouldn’t have ruined the surprise :p
was that horror indie flick filmed there?
why is that the surprise spot for our date?
you have 2 more questions left...choose wisely
why are we going to a cemetery?
are you really taking me somewhere else?
please tell me there isn’t a body in the trunk of your car
I don’t want to guess anymore
I don’t want to play anymore
